 editors]]\n[[Category:Politicians from Liverpool]]\n[[Category:People educated at Liverpool College]]\n[[Category:Knights Bachelor]]\n[[Category:Journalists from Liverpool]]\n[[Category:English male non-fiction writers]]\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_A._Willox"}
